{"id":501,"content":"```javascript\r\nfunction js2xml(originobj){\r\n    function render(key,value){\r\n      return `<${key}><![CDATA[${value}]]></${key}>`\r\n    }\r\n    function parsing(obj,nokey){\r\n      let result = ''\r\n      for(let key in obj){\r\n        if(Array.isArray(obj[key])){\r\n          obj[key].forEach(function(){\r\n            if(typeof obj[key] !== 'string'){\r\n              result += parsing(obj[key],true)\r\n            }else{\r\n              result += render(key,obj[key])\r\n            }\r\n          })\r\n        } else if(typeof obj[key] === 'object'){\r\n          if(nokey){\r\n            result += parsing(obj[key])\r\n          }else{\r\n            result += `<${key}>`\r\n            result += parsing(obj[key])\r\n            result += `</${key}>`\r\n          }\r\n        }\r\n        if(typeof obj[key] === 'string' || typeof obj[key] === 'number'){\r\n          result += render(key,obj[key])\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n      return result\r\n    }\r\n    return `<xml>${parsing(originobj)}</xml>`\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n每次写递归就有很爽的感觉","hide":"","time":"2018-12-06T05:08:05.000Z"}